title: Thor Son of Asgard
description:
Thor: Son of Asgard was a comic book series published by Marvel Comics in 2004 to 2005. It was originally a mini-series of 6 issues but was later extended to an ongoing series that lasted for 12 issues in total.

The series followed Thor\\\&#039;s early adventures in Asgard with Sif and Balder.

Its into three parts:
The Warriors Teen (1-6)
Enchanted (6-9)
Worthy (10-12)

Its a very good series and provides insight into early life of Thor. Enjoy and Seed.
